<h2 id="heading-0">Why Most Tech Stacks Fail</h2>

<p>Every software company promises the moon. "Automate everything!" "Save 10 hours a week!" "Never reconcile again!"</p>

<p>But here's what really happens:</p>

<ul>
<li>Tools don't talk to each other</li>
<li>Data gets stuck in silos</li>
<li>You spend more time managing tools than doing business</li>
<li>Monthly subscriptions add up to $500+/month</li>
</ul>

<p>After helping 200+ Texas businesses implement technology, we've found that simple, integrated stacks work better than complex "all-in-one" solutions.</p>

<p>Here's what we actually use and recommend.</p>

<h2 id="heading-1">The Core Accounting Foundation</h2>

<h3 id="heading-2">QuickBooks Online: Still the Best</h3>

<p><strong>Why we use it:</strong> 90% of our clients start here, and for good reason.</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Bank connections:</strong> 15,000+ banks supported</li>
<li><strong>Mobile app:</strong> Actually useful for expense tracking</li>
<li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Better than most alternatives</li>
<li><strong>Integration ecosystem:</strong> Works with everything</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> $30/month (Essentials), $200/month (Plus)</p>

<p><strong>Who it's for:</strong> Any business doing $500K+ annual revenue</p>

<h3 id="heading-3">Xero: The Challenger</h3>

<p><strong>When to choose Xero:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>You have multiple business entities</li>
<li>You need unlimited users</li>
<li>You want better inventory tracking</li>
<li>You prefer a cleaner interface</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> $15/month (Early), $70/month (Growing)</p>

<p><strong>Our take:</strong> Great for growing businesses, but QuickBooks has better bank connections in Texas.</p>

<h2 id="heading-4">Banking & Payments</h2>

<h3 id="heading-5">Plaid: The Data Pipeline</h3>

<p><strong>What it does:</strong> Connects your bank accounts to accounting software automatically.</p>

<p><strong>Why it matters:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>99.9% uptime:</strong> Transactions import reliably</li>
<li><strong>Real-time sync:</strong> See transactions within minutes</li>
<li><strong>Security:</strong> Bank-level encryption</li>
<li><strong>Texas banks:</strong> Works with all major Texas banks</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> Built into QuickBooks/Xero (no extra charge)</p>

<h3 id="heading-6">Stripe/Brevo: Payment Processing</h3>

<p><strong>Why we recommend Stripe:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Automatic reconciliation:</strong> Payments match invoices perfectly</li>
<li><strong>Fee transparency:</strong> 2.9% + 30¢ (no hidden fees)</li>
<li><strong>Texas compliance:</strong> Handles sales tax collection</li>
<li><strong>Integration:</strong> Direct QuickBooks sync</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Alternative:</strong> Brevo for businesses that need more features but less automation.</p>

<h2 id="heading-7">Expense Management</h2>

<h3 id="heading-8">Expensify: Receipts Made Simple</h3>

<p><strong>The problem:</strong> Expense reports take forever and are full of errors.</p>

<p><strong>The solution:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Mobile capture:</strong> Photo receipts automatically extract data</li>
<li><strong>Smart categorization:</strong> Learns your spending patterns</li>
<li><strong>Policy enforcement:</strong> Prevents overspending</li>
<li><strong>QuickBooks sync:</strong> One-click export</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> $0 for basic, $17/user/month for premium</p>

<p><strong>ROI:</strong> Saves 2-3 hours/week on expense reports</p>

<h3 id="heading-9">Zeni Finance: For Growing Teams</h3>

<p><strong>When to upgrade:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>You have 5+ employees submitting expenses</li>
<li>You need approval workflows</li>
<li>You want corporate card integration</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> Custom pricing (starts at $12/user/month)</p>

<h2 id="heading-10">Time Tracking & Invoicing</h2>

<h3 id="heading-11">Harvest: Time Tracking Done Right</h3>

<p><strong>Why it works:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><strong>One-click timers:</strong> Start/stop tracking without thinking</li>
<li><strong>Project budgets:</strong> See profitability in real-time</li>
<li><strong>Invoice generation:</strong> Creates invoices from tracked time</li>
<li><strong>QuickBooks sync:</strong> Time entries import automatically</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> $12/user/month</p>

<p><strong>Who needs it:</strong> Service businesses, consultants, agencies</p>

<h3 id="heading-12">Pilot: Invoicing Automation</h3>

<p><strong>For businesses that:</strong></p>

<ul>
